# Railyard SPEC maintenance

[`docs/SPEC.md`](docs/SPEC.md) is the canonical product/architecture specification.

When you implement or change features in this repo (orchestrator, board UI, workstreams, routing, runtimes, APIs, settings, security, jobs, connectors):

1. Update `docs/SPEC.md` in the same change set — matching sections and the Version date.
2. Update `README.md` / focused `docs/*.md` if the operator-facing entry points changed.
3. Do not claim unverified build/test results in SPEC.

If a task is docs-only for SPEC, still leave the Version date accurate.
